gas in those bubbles.

812
01:04:55,191 --> 01:04:56,059
I, uh,

813
01:04:57,093 --> 01:04:58,294
think I'll go this way.

814
01:04:59,095 --> 01:05:00,063
So watch your step.

815
01:05:00,698 --> 01:05:01,599
You stay close.

816
01:05:21,985 --> 01:05:22,686
What is this place?

817
01:05:23,353 --> 01:05:24,588
Ice shanties.

818
01:05:24,622 --> 01:05:26,122
They call it the Empty Quarter.

819
