anything about my connection?

828
01:06:07,330 --> 01:06:09,432
You're a weekend tour guide.

829
01:06:09,466 --> 01:06:10,568
You sold out.

830
01:06:11,769 --> 01:06:13,637
I'm protecting our home.

831
01:06:13,671 --> 01:06:16,707
-I'm protecting what belongs to
all of us.
-Well you lost all of us.

832
01:06:18,274 --> 01:06:20,644
Why don't you help yourself
to some food back there?

833
01:06:20,678 --> 01:06:22,312
Take all you want. We have lots.

834
