-Listen I-I wanna--
-How dare you

857
01:08:19,530 --> 01:08:22,498
bring your fucking
poison back here to my land?

858
01:08:25,501 --> 01:08:26,604
Listen, um--

859
01:08:27,705 --> 01:08:29,172
I want you to know that
the crew that's chasing us,

860
01:08:29,205 --> 01:08:33,242
