1017
01:19:09,412 --> 01:19:10,280
Harlan!

1018
01:19:11,481 --> 01:19:12,949
Ahhh!

1019
01:19:12,983 --> 01:19:13,950
Harlan!

1020
01:19:13,984 --> 01:19:15,485
-Ani?
-Ahhh!

1021
01:19:41,444 --> 01:19:42,345
Ani?

1022
01:19:48,985 --> 01:19:49,853
