1048
01:20:58,656 --> 01:20:59,523
Ah!

1049
01:21:01,091 --> 01:21:01,958
Ah!

1050
01:21:03,193 --> 01:21:04,127
Ugh!

1051
01:21:05,495 --> 01:21:06,363
Ugh!

1052
